{"tid":919363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[強姦金] 積金局連蝕8年錢 擬MPF徵年費填氹","createTime":"2018-11-28T03:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T20:05:35.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"72ad0c9e4a06617150974be1246c67cddad35767","tid":919363,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T03:52:22.000Z","msg":"積金局連續虧蝕8年，擬向MPF徵年費填氹。《信報》引述消息，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政府正計劃向強積金受託人所管理的資產徵收0.05%註冊年費，以9月底強積金總資產8583.14億元計，涉款每年可達4.3億元</strong></span>；以積金局至今年3月年度蝕2.49億計，計劃落實後積金局將「一炮過」扭虧為盈。由於牽涉修訂法例，料最快2020後才可實行。<br />\n<br />\n保險業界立法會議員陳健波向《信報》表示，業界質疑費用過於龐大，又會隨MPF資產總額擴大而增加，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>且不准轉嫁成本至打工仔，反指積金局應控制開支，擔心當局一蝕錢就會繼續加徵收費</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n積金局指計劃為政府決定，又稱當局靠政府1998年時撥出的50億元補助金的投資收益營運，原本估計只夠運作10年，但當局嚴守財務紀律，至今已運作20年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181128/58967358\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58967358&d=uNoWp92JVkE6MadDRBf1OBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=5da226ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181128%2F58967358&h=90edb952\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181128/58967358</a>"},{"pid":"464c09448f829ad69c4f080336efa1066999fb9c","tid":919363,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:14:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>向強積金受託人所管理的資產徵收0.05%註冊年費...且不准轉嫁成本至打工仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁即係收FUND佬"},{"pid":"3c6bd7bb0ddcf236d4717f9dbed0e4ed34cd80dd","tid":919363,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T18:16:58.000Z","msg":"積金局會唔會冇錢供mpf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ecbcfbb33c4779633e88f4edffee8d8c9b367ee","tid":919363,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"464c09